---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="AMRs — Formic"
  description="Autonomous mobile robots for pallet and tote movement. Dock to staging, line to wrap — under Formic Full Service."
  ogTitle="AMRs — Formic"
  ogDescription="Pallet movement without forklifts. AMR fleets deployed under Formic Full Service."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/solutions/amrs" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/solutions">Solutions</a><span class="sep">/</span>AMRs
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">AMRs</div>
    <h1>Pallet movement<br><em>without forklifts.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">AMR fleets that handle pallet and tote movement between zones — dock to staging, line to wrap, finished goods to outbound. Running alongside your team, not in place of it, and dramatically reducing forklift-related injuries and product damage.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/AMR-warehouse.jpg">
        <source src="/RFA_header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-fpo">FPO</span>
      <span class="dv-cap">AMR fleet · production cycle</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Why It Matters</div>
      <h2>Forklifts are <em>the silent cost</em>.</h2>
      <p>Forklifts run up the highest single-source injury bill on most CPG and warehousing floors. They damage pallets, damage racking, and damage product. AMRs replace the routine, repeating moves — your forklift drivers focus on exception work and inbound.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Significant reduction in forklift-related injury claims</li>
        <li>Lower pallet and product damage in transit</li>
        <li>Frees forklift drivers for inbound and exception work</li>
        <li>Predictable cycle times for line-side replenishment</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Scope my floor →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/AMR-warehouse.jpg" alt="AMR moving a pallet through a warehouse" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Autonomous · pallet handling</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/AMR-warehouse.jpg">
        <source src="/RFA_header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="img-cap">Dynamic routing · safe-by-design</span>
    </div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — How It Works</div>
      <h2>Routes that <em>adapt</em>.</h2>
      <p>SLAM-based navigation — no floor tape, no embedded wires. The fleet adapts to pallet placement and floor traffic in real time. WMS and ERP integration keeps inventory state synchronized as the AMRs move.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Dynamic routing — adapts to changing floor layouts</li>
        <li>Integrated with WMS and ERP for real-time inventory tracking</li>
        <li>Safe by design — slows and stops around humans automatically</li>
        <li>Mixed traffic with manual forklifts and pedestrians</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">03 — Specs</div>
      <h2>Fleets that <em>scale</em>.</h2>
      <p>Start with two AMRs, scale to thirty. Add capacity as your pallet flow grows — same software, same fleet manager, same SLA.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Fleet sizes from 2 to 30+ AMRs</li>
        <li>Payloads: up to 1,500 kg per unit, larger options available</li>
        <li>Battery: opportunity charging, no shift-end swaps</li>
        <li>Integration: WMS, ERP, MES via REST or message-bus</li>
        <li>Safety: ANSI/RIA R15.08 mobile robot compliant</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">See AMR fleets →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="AMR fleet in production" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Fleet · scaled deployment</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/Talos-0143.jpg">
        <source src="/RFA_header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-fpo">FPO</span>
      <span class="dv-cap">Fleet routing · production day</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Move pallets<br><em>without moving people.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/solutions" class="btn-ctawh">All Solutions</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
